<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_91_r1l6">Arnolt phılıps ſune </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l7">von ~ Hengſperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_91_line_1577026745522_4880"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Arnolt ~ Als du vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt von vvılhalm Beren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Alſo haben vvır Jn beſandt / Vnd darumb cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l10">red geſacʒt ~ der hat vns geantvvürt / vvıe er der ſach vnſchuldıg ſeÿ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l11">vvıe darumb bedarfft du eins geleÿts / das vvellen vvır dır gern <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l12">hiecʒvviſchen vnd den cʒehen tagen in der vaſten ſchiriſt / cʒu vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l13">beÿ vns / vnd von vns / für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l14"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> valentinj <expan>A<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
